NK100(the)012:1: // rdzogs pa chen po stobs gsum gyi gdams ngag gi bsdus don sogs chos tshan dgu bzhugs so //
NK100(the)012:3: san t+ai ma h+aa tsi ta gar+b+ha pa la t+r+ai u pa d+he sha na ma /
NK100(the)012:5: rdzogs pa chen po thugs kyi snying po stobs gsum gyi gdams ngag zhes bya ba /
NK100(the)012:6: sku gsum ston pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK100(the)012:7: rdzogs chen gdams ngag stobs gsum gyis /
NK100(the)012:8: gdul bya rnams gsum drang pa'i phyir /
NK100(the)012:9: ston pa gsum gyis gsungs pa bzhin /
NK100(the)012:10: phyi rabs drang phyir bshad par bya /
NK100(the)012:11: de la rdzogs pa chen po snyan rgyud thugs kyi
NK100(the)012:12: snying po'i gdams ngag gi stobs gsum gyis gdul bya
NK100(the)012:14: gzhung bshad pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK100(the)012:15: dkyus dgrol ba'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyis drang ba dang /
NK100(the)012:16: rgol phyir rgol brtsod pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK100(the)012:17: skyon bsal ba'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyi drang pa dang /
NK100(the)012:18: byang chub bsgrub pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK100(the)012:19: nyams su blang pa'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyis drang pa'o //
NK100(the)012:20: gzhung bshad pa la drug /dkyus kyi khog gzhung la
NK100(the)012:21: mkhas pa bya'i phyir na khog dbub pa'i gdams ngag
NK100(the)012:22: /dkyus kyi rnam dbye la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir
NK100(the)012:23: na / sa bcad pa'i gdams ngag /dkyus kyi ngo ti la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:24: 'bru gzhom pa'i gdams ngag /dkyus kyi brgal lan la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:25: dri ba lan gyi gdams ngag /dkyus kyi 'gro sa la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:26: mthar thug grub mtha'i gdams ngag /dkyus dgrol ba'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyis drang pa dang /
NK100(the)012:27: brtsod pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK100(the)012:28: skyon bsal ba'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyis drang pa dang /
NK100(the)012:29: byang chub bsgrub pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK100(the)012:30: nyams su blang pa'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyis drang pa'o //
NK100(the)012:31: gzhung bshad pa la drug /dkyus kyi khog gzhung la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:32: khog dbub pa'i gdams ngag /dkyus kyi rnam dbye la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:33: sa bcad gdams ngi ngag /dkyus kyo ti la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:34: 'bru gzhom pa'i gdams ngag /dkyus kyi rgal lan la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:35: dri ba lan gyi gdams ngag /dkyus kyi 'gro so la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:36: mthar thug grub mtha'i gdams ngag /dkyus kyi nyams su blangs la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)012:37: lam du bslang ba'i gdams ngag go //
NK100(the)012:38: rgod phyir rgol brtson pa la drug /chos can /
NK100(the)012:43: byang chub bsgrub pa la gsum /
NK100(the)012:44: thun mong spyi'i gdams ngag /khyad par gyi gdams ngag /bsdu ba 'jig gi gdams ngag go //
NK100(the)012:46: thog mar sngon du 'gro ba'i gdams ngag /tha mar rang rgyud gdul ba'i man ngag go //
NK100(the)012:49: bar du dad pa bskyed pa /
NK100(the)012:50: tha mar bla ma bsten pa'o //
NK100(the)012:54: thob par dka' bar brtag pa'o //
NK100(the)012:56: ma nyams pa bdun dang ldan pa ste /
NK100(the)012:64: rten nyams pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)012:65: ngan song gsum gyi sems can no //
NK100(the)012:66: ma nyams pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)012:68: gling nyams pa ni gling chen po gsum dang gling chung brgyad do //
NK100(the)012:69: ma nyams pa 'dzam bu'i gling ngo //
NK100(the)012:70: gnas nyams pa mon dang kla klo'i gnas so //
NK100(the)012:71: ma nyam pa rgya gar rdo rje gdan la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)012:72: dbang po nyams pa 'on dig long ba la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)012:73: ma nyams pa dbang po la skyon med pa'o //
NK100(the)012:74: shes pa nyams pa rlung dang lha 'dres dbang byas pa'o //
NK100(the)012:75: ma nyams pa shes pa rang dbang thob pa'o //
NK100(the)012:76: las nyams pa sdig pa'i phyogs su mos shing gzhol ba'o //
NK100(the)012:77: ma nyams pa dge ba'i phyogs su mos shing gus pa'o //
NK100(the)012:78: las kyi mtha' log pa sngon la chos byas byas mjug mi chos byed pa'o //
NK100(the)012:79: ma logs pa dam pa'i chos mthar phyin pa'o //
NK100(the)012:80: 'byor pa ni snang ba ma log pa bdun dang ldan pa ste /
NK100(the)012:81: bde bar gshegs pa lung gi snang ba ma log pa dur mo la ngar yod pa lta bu /
NK100(the)012:82: bla ma bka'i snang ba ma log pa mkhregs rdo la zur yod pa lta bu /
NK100(the)012:83: rang shes rab kyi snang ba ma log pa btsa' la brlan ma zhugs pa lta bu /
NK100(the)012:84: mtshams sbyor bar byed pa dus kyi snang ba ma
NK100(the)012:85: log pa snga phyi dus gcig gis bsdus pa lta
NK100(the)012:86: bu / bya ba dang byed pa las kyi snang
NK100(the)012:87: ba ma log pa 'tshogs pa'i rdzas la skyes bu
NK100(the)012:88: lag gi rtsol ba zhugs pa lta bu'o //
NK100(the)012:89: yo byad rgyu'i snang ba ma log pa shing gi bungs cher yod pa lta bu /
NK100(the)012:90: mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i snang ba ma log pa
NK100(the)012:91: sreg 'tshed kyi bya ba byed pa'i me lta bu'o
NK100(the)012:92: // yo byad kyi rgyu lnga la /
NK100(the)012:98: thob par dka' ba la gsum /
NK100(the)012:99: thob par dka' ba'i gtan tshigs ma thob pa'i skyon /
NK100(the)012:101: gtan tshigs ni dus gsum du nyams log gnyis 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK100(the)012:102: dal 'byor phun sum 'tshogs pa de thob par dka' bar brtag go //
NK100(the)012:104: dka' ba de thob rung ma thob rung snyam na /
NK100(the)012:105: dal 'byor ma thob na 'bras bu bsgrub pa'i thabs med skyon /
NK100(the)012:106: thabs de yod rung med rung snyam na /
NK100(the)012:107: thabs 'di la ma brten na byang chub kyi sems bu mi thob pa'i skyon /
NK100(the)012:108: 'bras bu de thob rung ma thob rung snyam na /
NK100(the)012:109: 'bras bu ma thob na 'khor bar 'khyam pa'i skyon /
NK100(the)012:110: 'khor bar 'khyams rung ma 'khyams rung snyam na /
NK100(the)012:111: 'khor bar 'khyams na 'khor ba la nyes dmigs 'byung ba'i skyon /
NK100(the)012:112: nyes dmigs 'byung na 'khor ba bzhag pas chog snyam na /
NK100(the)012:113: nyes dmigs byung tsam na 'khor bar bzhag dka' ba'i skyon no //
NK100(the)012:115: 'khor ba'i gnas la btson ra lta bu'i nyes dmigs /
NK100(the)012:116: rgyud la skye ba'i nyon mongs pa la srin bu lta bu /
NK100(the)012:117: sdig pa las spyod pa la tsan dug la spyod pa lta bu /
NK100(the)012:118: rnyed pa dang bskur bsti la snyi dang rgya lta bu /
NK100(the)012:119: sdang ba'i dgra lan nad gdugs pa can nam rims mi zad pa lta bu /
NK100(the)012:120: gdung pa'i gnyen la 'khor ba'i bshal thag lta bu /
NK100(the)012:121: zang zing gi nor la byur gyi gdos lta bu /
NK100(the)012:122: mi lus la sgyu ma lta bu /
NK100(the)012:123: mi tshe la chu bur lta bu'o //
NK100(the)012:124: bzhag dka' ba'i skyon la dgu /
NK100(the)012:127: ma brtags pa'i 'khor ba nyams dga' ba /
NK100(the)012:129: nyon mongs pa dbang che ba /
NK100(the)012:132: ma rtogs pa'i rgya mtsho gting ring pa /
NK100(the)012:133: sngon byas las kyi 'khor lo shugs drag pa'o //
NK100(the)012:135: dal bas chos byar khom pa /
NK100(the)012:136: 'byor pas chos spyod du yod pa'o //
NK100(the)012:137: snyan brgyud thugs kyi snying po las /
NK100(the)012:138: dal 'byor brtag pa'i le'u ste dang po'o ////dad pa bskyed pa la bdun /
NK100(the)012:139: dad pa rang sa nas mtshon la /
NK100(the)012:145: dad pa'i gol sa dgag pa'o //
NK100(the)012:146: rang sa nas mtshon pa la bzhi /
NK100(the)012:150: ngo bo ni rang gi shes pa dang po'i bdag
NK100(the)012:151: nyid las dge ba dang thug gis phrad pa de'o
NK100(the)012:152: // nges tshig ni dkar phyogs su dad pa'i phyir dad pa'o //
NK100(the)012:157: mos pa'i dad pas rjes su 'brang /
NK100(the)012:158: dang ba'i dad pas mi mthun pa'i phyogs sel /
NK100(the)012:159: yid ches pa'i dad pas de la sur gyis 'jug
NK100(the)012:160: /mthar phyiin pa'i dad pas de las mi ldog pa'o
NK100(the)012:162: dge ba tshang zhing rdzogs pas smin cing grol bar byed pa /
NK100(the)012:163: sdig pa mi gnas shing mi dmigs par byed pa'o //
NK100(the)012:164: skyon ni med pa skyon gyi des drug /dad pa med pa'i gang zag de //
NK100(the)012:165: rgya mtsho'i gting gi pha bong 'dra //
NK100(the)012:166: gru la gnyan pa med pa 'dra //
NK100(the)012:167: lag rdum gser gling phyin pa 'dra //
NK100(the)012:168: long pa lha khang blta ba 'dra //
NK100(the)012:172: rgyud bzhi la brten te btsal /
NK100(the)012:173: bla ma'i rgyud la brten te dad pa btsal ba /
NK100(the)012:174: bka'i rang gi 'gro ba gzhan gyi'o //
NK100(the)012:176: bla ma'i mdzad spyod la brten te dad pa btsal ba /
NK100(the)012:179: bka' drang don la brten te dad pa btsal ba /
NK100(the)012:182: rang dal 'byor phun sum tshogs pa la brten te dad pa btsal ba /
NK100(the)012:183: mi rtag pa rgyud la skyes pa la'o //
NK100(the)012:185: gzhan bde ba phun sum 'tshogs pa la brten te dad pa btsal ba /
NK100(the)012:186: sdug bsngal phun sum tshogs pa la'o //
NK100(the)012:187: yon tan ni yod pa yon tan gyi dpe drug /dad pa yod pa'i gang zag de /
NK100(the)012:188: dper na sa gzhi gshin pa 'dra /
NK100(the)012:189: chu bo sgrol ba'i gru dang 'dra /
NK100(the)012:193: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen 'dra'o //
NK100(the)012:194: mtshang ni dad pa rang gi rgyud la yang ma skyes btsal bas kyang ma rnyed na /
NK100(the)012:195: bgrang pa mtshang gi dpe drug /srog ma chad pa'i ro yin /
NK100(the)012:196: chang ma mthungs pa'i ra ro ba /
NK100(the)012:197: lha 'dres ma bslabs pa'i bsnyo ba /
NK100(the)012:198: sug bzhi sa la mi 'dzugs pa'i byol song /
NK100(the)012:199: khyo ga ji ltar yon tan ldan yang dad pa
NK100(the)012:200: gtings med na glang gser gyi snal chu can yin
NK100(the)012:201: / bud med ji ltar yon tan ldan yang dad
NK100(the)012:202: pa gtings med na g.yu'i khog thag can yin no
NK100(the)012:203: / // thabs ni dad pa rgyud rgyud la brten
NK100(the)012:204: pa'i thabs drug /dad pa skye ba'i yul la bsten
NK100(the)012:205: / // te skyer gzhug / 'phel ba'i rgyu bzhi la brten te spel /
NK100(the)012:206: 'grib pa'i rkyen bzhi'i khar mi gtang /
NK100(the)012:207: yod pa'i rtags bzhis gcan la bal /
NK100(the)012:208: byed pa'i las bzhis mthar byung /
NK100(the)012:209: mthun pa'i song bzhis nye bar mtshon no //
NK100(the)012:211: chos pa'i dad pa skye ba'i yul ni /
NK100(the)012:212: sangs rgyas chos dang bla ma gsum la brten nas skye /
NK100(the)012:213: dang ba'i dad pa skye ba'i yul ni /
NK100(the)012:214: nyon mongs pa dug lnga chos nyid du shes pa la bsten nas skye /
NK100(the)012:215: yid ches pa'i dad pa skye ba'i yul ni /
NK100(the)012:216: las rgyu 'bras la bsten nas skye /
NK100(the)012:217: mthar phyin pa'i dad pa skye ba'i yul ni /
NK100(the)012:218: dad pa de rnams rang gi rgyud la tshang zhing 'tshogs pa las skye'o //
NK100(the)012:220: bla ma dam pa yun du bsten cing mos gus tshud na dad pa 'phel /
NK100(the)012:221: grogs khyad par can gyi mdzad spyod la brten na /
NK100(the)012:222: mdo lung zab mo'i lta rtog la brten na /
NK100(the)012:223: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches mi rtag pa rgyud la skyes na'o //
NK100(the)012:225: bla ma dam pa'i mdzad spyod log na dad pa 'grib /
NK100(the)012:226: chos pa spyi'i spyod pa log na dad pa 'grib /
NK100(the)012:228: mi chos kyi bya ba thog tu babs na'o //
NK100(the)012:230: rang thos bsam gyi shes rab la 'bad rtsol che
NK100(the)012:231: zhing rgyud sbyong pa la nan tan che na dad
NK100(the)012:233: bla ma dang yi dam gyi lha la mos gus kyi gdung ba che na /
NK100(the)012:234: sdig pa 'phra mo la yang 'dzems pa che na /
NK100(the)012:235: dge ba 'phra mo nas nyams len byed na'o //
NK100(the)012:237: dge sbyor thams cad kyi rten byed /
NK100(the)012:239: man ngag thams cad kyi snod /
NK100(the)012:240: shes rab thams cad kyi 'dzin no //
NK100(the)012:242: mos pa'i dad pa bu ma phyir 'breng pa 'dra /
NK100(the)012:243: dang ba'i dad pa nor bu chu dang chu'i rnyog pa sel ba /
NK100(the)012:244: yid ches pa'i dad pas rdo'i nang nas rin po che rnyed pa /
NK100(the)012:245: mthar phyin pa'i dad pa rin po che'i nang nas
NK100(the)012:246: gser sa le sbram dang g.yu spu ris can 'chang
NK100(the)012:247: ba'o // dad pa'i gol sa dgag pa la drug /bo ba dang brlag pa gnyis /
NK100(the)012:249: byer ba dang zug pa gnyis /
NK100(the)012:250: de rnams su mi gtang pa'o //
NK100(the)012:252: dad pa rang sar bo ba dang /
NK100(the)012:255: rang gi dad pa'i stobs kyis dge sbyor dum gcig byas des tshim pa'o //
NK100(the)012:256: gnyis pa ni dge sbyor cig bya bar 'dod pa la sdig par kha 'khyogs pa'o //
NK100(the)012:258: dang po dad pa yod dus su dge sbyor ma
NK100(the)012:259: byas de nas dad pa gtings skyer ma bstub pa'o
NK100(the)012:261: dang po dad pa dum cig yod pa la de je chung je chung song pa'o //
NK100(the)012:263: dad pa'i stobs kyis dge sbyor byas pa las nga rgyal gyi dbang gis sems khengs pa'o //
NK100(the)012:265: dge sbyor byas na ma byas de'ang bya'am snyam pa'i blo tshab tshub pa de'o //
NK100(the)012:267: dge sbyor ngos bzung pa de ma grub na 'jog pa'o //
NK100(the)012:268: snyan rgyud thugs kyi snying po las /
NK100(the)012:269: dad pa bskyed pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o ////bla ma brten pa la brgyad /
NK100(the)012:270: dgos pa sgo gsum gyi sgo nas bla ma dam pa gcig la brten dgos pa /
NK100(the)012:271: bla ma dam pa gang la byas pa'i mtshan nyid brtag pa /
NK100(the)012:272: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i bla ma bsten pa'i rdzas bsags pa /
NK100(the)012:273: sogs nas gces pa tshul drug gi sgo nas bla ma de btsal ba /
NK100(the)012:274: rnyed nas bya ba srol lnga'i sgo nas bla ma bsten pa /
NK100(the)012:275: bsten nas bla ma la bsnyen bkur ji ltar bya ba /
NK100(the)012:276: byas nas bla ma la gdams ngag gi zhu tshul /
NK100(the)012:277: de ltar bla ma bsten pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK100(the)012:278: dgos pa gsum gyi sgo nas bla ma dam pa gcig la bsten dgos pa ni /
NK100(the)012:279: byang chub kyi 'bras bu bsgrub na /
NK100(the)012:280: dang po blo gros dri bar bya ba'i rgyu bla ma yin par brten dgos pa /
NK100(the)012:281: bar du shes rab 'phel bar byed pa'i rkyen bla ma yin pas /
NK100(the)012:282: tha ma rang gang du 'gro ba shes par mdzad mkhan bla ma yin pas so //
NK100(the)012:283: mtshan nyid brtag pa la gnyis /
NK100(the)012:284: thun mong gi bla ma mtshan nyid drug ldan dang /
NK100(the)012:285: thun mong ma yin pa'i bla ma mtshan nyid drug ldan no //
NK100(the)012:286: dang po ni khungs nas byung ba'i lung dang ldan pa /
NK100(the)012:287: thos bsam gyi shes rab la rgyud 'byongs pa /
NK100(the)012:288: gtan la phebs pa'i rig pa khong du shar ba /
NK100(the)012:289: phyin ci ma log pa'i gdams ngag ston shes pa /
NK100(the)012:290: 'gro ba'i don la brtson 'grus che ba /
NK100(the)012:291: thugs rje la dbre bsnan chung pa'o //
NK100(the)012:292: gnyis pa ni rtogs pa'i lta ba khyad du mi gsod pa'i bla ma /
NK100(the)012:293: nyams myong gi bsgom pa yal bar mi 'dor ba /
NK100(the)012:294: bya byed kyi spyod pa la gzhung ma log pa /
NK100(the)012:295: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu mngon du snang ba /
NK100(the)012:297: phyi ma 'ba' zhig don du gnyer ba'o //
NK100(the)012:300: dad pa skye 'bri med pa chu bo'i gzhung lta bu /
NK100(the)012:301: brtson 'grus thung lhod med pa gzhu gdungs pa'i rgyud lta bu /
NK100(the)012:302: dam tshig la 'gyur ldog med par gser sa le sbram lta bu'o //
NK100(the)012:303: gces pa drug gi sgo nas bla ma btsal ba ni /
NK100(the)012:304: rgyus med pa'i lta bur gces pas /
NK100(the)012:305: rgyus med lam pa tshor ba lta bur bla ma btsal ba /
NK100(the)012:306: mi shi'i skyel ma lta bur gces pas /
NK100(the)012:307: mi sha skyes ma tshol ba /
NK100(the)012:308: mtshon skyob pa'i go lta bur gces pas /
NK100(the)012:309: 'khrug pa la go cha tshol ba /
NK100(the)012:310: nad gso ba'i sman pa lta bur gces pas /
NK100(the)012:312: mun pa sel ba'i sgron me lta bur ces pas /
NK100(the)012:313: nam la sgron me tshol ba /
NK100(the)012:314: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i nor bu lta bur gces pas /
NK100(the)012:315: ded dpon nor bu tshol ba'o //
NK100(the)012:316: bya ba srol lnga'i sgo nas bla ma bsten pa ni /
NK100(the)012:317: theg pa che ba sa gzhi'i srol gyis bla ma bsten pa /
NK100(the)012:318: dri lan mi rtsi ba gru'i /
NK100(the)012:320: mos pa ma phyi na bu'i /
NK100(the)012:321: snyan pa rgyal po gdan la bzhugs po'o //
NK100(the)012:322: bsnyen bskur bya ba la gsum /
NK100(the)012:323: sgo gsum dang ba'i bsnyen bkur bya ba /
NK100(the)012:326: dang po ni lus kyi sgo nas bla ma la bskor ba dang lha phyag rgyun mi bcad /
NK100(the)012:327: ngag gi sgo nas rjes dang bstod sgra /
NK100(the)012:328: yid kyi sgo nas brtse ba gdung ba'o //
NK100(the)012:330: dgos pa'i dam pa rang gi zhing khang yang bla ma la dbul /
NK100(the)012:331: gces pa'i dam pa mchan gyi bu smad yang bzhed na bla ma la dbul /
NK100(the)012:332: nor gyi dbyig gser dngul dang zangs lcags /
NK100(the)012:333: rta dang glang po 'bru'i bang mdzod /
NK100(the)012:334: gos kyi kha dog /zas kyi ro mchog la sogs
NK100(the)012:335: pa ci bzhed pa bla ma la chags pa med
NK100(the)012:336: par dbul lo // bsgrub pa la gsum /
NK100(the)012:337: rab lta thog nas bsgrub nus pa /
NK100(the)012:338: 'bring bsgom thog nas bsgrub nus pa /
NK100(the)012:339: tha ma spyod thog nas bsgrub nus pa'o //
NK100(the)012:340: gdams ngag gi zhu tshul la gnyis /
NK100(the)012:341: log pa'i mthong lugs rnam pa lnga spangs la zhu ba /
NK100(the)012:342: yang dag pa'i go lugs rnam pa lnga dang ldan par zhu ba'o //
NK100(the)012:347: grogs mtshungs par spyod pa la dgrar /
NK100(the)012:348: nan tan gdams ngag go nas spyod pa de tshe ma phyid du'o //
NK100(the)012:353: grogs mtshungs par spyod pa la nad g.yog tu /
NK100(the)012:354: nan tan gdams ngag go nas spyod pa de nad sos par ro //
NK100(the)012:355: bla ma bsten pa'i dgos pa la gsum /
NK100(the)012:356: bla ma dam pa cig bsten pas 'jig rten gyi
NK100(the)012:357: kha na ma tho ba dang bcas pa mi 'byung
NK100(the)012:358: ba'i dgos pa / de ma byung pas bla ma la dad pa 'phel 'grib med pa'i dgos pa /
NK100(the)012:359: de med pas 'chi ka dang srid pa bar do
NK100(the)012:360: dang tshe phyi ma la yang bla ma de'i snang
NK100(the)012:361: ba 'char cing 'dren pa mdzad pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK100(the)012:362: snyan rgyud thugs kyi snying po las /
NK100(the)012:363: bla ma bsten pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o ////rang rgyud
NK100(the)012:364: gdul ba la drug /mi rtag pa brgyud la bskyed
NK100(the)012:365: de rang gi rgyud gdul ba /
NK100(the)012:366: glen pa rgyud las spangs te rang gi rgyud gdul ba /
NK100(the)012:367: dka' ba rgyud la bsgril te rang gi rgyud gdul ba /
NK100(the)012:368: mi ldan pa'i blo rgyud bzlog ste rang gi rgyud gdul ba /
NK100(the)012:369: ldan pa'i shes rab rgyud la sbyangs te rang gi rgyud gdul ba /
NK100(the)012:370: nan tan gyi gdams ngag rgyud la mnan te rang rgyud gdul ba'o //
NK100(the)012:371: mi rtag pa rgyud la bskyed pa la bzhi ste /
NK100(the)012:372: dngos po gang mi rtag dpe ci dang 'dra ba rtag pa /
NK100(the)012:373: tshul gang gi sgo nas mi rtag pa /
NK100(the)012:374: mi rtag pa rgyud la skyes pa'i phan yon nam dgos pa'o //
NK100(the)012:375: dngos po gang mi rtag na /
NK100(the)012:376: snod bcud gnyis las 'dir bcud kyi sems can mi rtag pa gtsor ston //
NK100(the)012:377: dpe ci dang 'dra bar mi rtag na /
NK100(the)012:378: lus ni mi rtag g.yang sa'i sdong gog 'dra //
NK100(the)012:379: dbugs ni mi rtag la kha'i na bun 'dra //
NK100(the)012:380: yid ni mi rtag nam mkha'i glog dang 'dra //
NK100(the)012:381: tshe ni mi rtag rtsa kha'i zil pa 'dra'o //
NK100(the)012:382: tshul gang gi sgo nas mi rtag na /
NK100(the)012:383: 'chi ba bzhi sbrag gi tshul gyis mi rtag /
NK100(the)012:386: 'chi ba la cis kyang mi gtongs pa /
NK100(the)012:389: sngar lus pa med pas 'chi nges /
NK100(the)012:391: tshe skad cig ma gcig tu mi sdod pas /
NK100(the)012:392: byas pa thams cad mi rtag pas so //
NK100(the)012:394: tshe la nges pa med pas nam 'chi cha med /
NK100(the)012:395: lus la snying po med pas /
NK100(the)012:397: snang ba brtag mi bzod pas so //
NK100(the)012:398: 'chi ba la cis kyang mi gtongs pa'i chos bzhi /
NK100(the)012:399: brtsigs pa'i gnas kyis 'chi ba la mi gtongs /
NK100(the)012:402: rang lus kyi sgo yis so //
NK100(the)012:403: 'chi ba rang gi dngos po'i chos bzhi /
NK100(the)012:404: mal gos kyi tha ma na nyal /
NK100(the)012:405: gnyen 'dun gyi tha mas bskor ba /
NK100(the)012:406: za chu'i tha ma za ba /
NK100(the)012:407: gtam gyi tha ma smra ba'o //
NK100(the)012:408: de rnams kyi chings bzhi la /
NK100(the)012:409: 'chi nges pas chos bya bar la thag bcad /
NK100(the)012:410: nam 'chi cha med pas chos la phyir bshol mi gdab /
NK100(the)012:411: 'chi ba la ci byas kyang mi gtongs pas chos rkyen dbang du mi gtang /
NK100(the)012:412: 'chi ba rang gi dngos po thog gsum nas gshigs shing ces gsum dang ldan par bya'o //
NK100(the)012:414: 'chi bas mi 'jigs pa'i chos dang ldan /
NK100(the)012:416: 'chi ba la brod pa'i chos dang ldan /
NK100(the)012:417: tha ma spyod thog nas 'chi ste /
NK100(the)012:418: 'chi kar mi 'gyod pa'i chos dang ldan no //
NK100(the)012:419: phan yon nam dgos pa la bzhi /
NK100(the)012:422: chags sdang myur du zhi bar byed /
NK100(the)012:423: mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs sla'o //
NK100(the)012:424: glen pa rgyud la spangs pa la glen pa'i mdo bzhi /
NK100(the)012:426: bdag tu bzung ba'i glen pa gsum /
NK100(the)012:427: bdag gir bzung ba'i glen pa gsum /
NK100(the)012:428: bya byed las kyi glen pa gnyis /
NK100(the)012:429: mthar thug don la glen pa gcig go //
NK100(the)012:430: bdag tu bzung ba'i glen pa gsum ni /
NK100(the)012:431: rang lus mi rtag sgyu ma la /
NK100(the)012:432: lhag pa'i bsnyen bkur byed pa de shin tu glen /
NK100(the)012:433: mi lus 'di'i sdug bsngal phra mo mi bzod par /
NK100(the)012:434: ngan song sdug bsngal bzod la re ba /
NK100(the)012:435: sdug bsngal chen po nam yong cha med par /
NK100(the)012:436: tshe 'di rtag par bzung nas nya ra byed pa'o //
NK100(the)012:437: bdag gir bzung ba'i glen pa gsum ni /
NK100(the)012:438: dgra mi rtag sgyu ma la /
NK100(the)012:439: lhag pa'i zhe sdang byed na shin tu glen /
NK100(the)012:440: gnyen mi rtag sgyu ma la /
NK100(the)012:441: lhag pa'i gdung pa byed na /
NK100(the)012:442: nor mi rtag sgyu ma la /
NK100(the)012:443: lhag pa'i zhen chags byed na'o //
NK100(the)012:444: bya byed las kyi glen pa gnyis ni /
NK100(the)012:445: don yod dge ba bcu po gzhung du mi spyod par /
NK100(the)012:446: don med 'khrul pa'i las la g.yengs pa shin tu glen /
NK100(the)012:447: mi lus gtsang ma rin chen 'di thob nas /
NK100(the)012:448: byang chub kyi 'bras bu myur du mi bsgrub par /
NK100(the)012:449: rang gis sdug bsngal shom pa de shin du glen no //
NK100(the)012:450: mthar thug don la glen pa chen po /
NK100(the)012:451: bden pa'i thig le gcig la mi bsdud par /
NK100(the)012:452: mtshon pa tshig gi mtha' la zhen pa de shin tu glen no //
NK100(the)012:453: dka' ba rgyud la bsgrib pa la dka' ba dgu ni /
NK100(the)012:454: dang por rdzogs pa chen po'i gdams ngag gi rten
NK100(the)012:455: gtsang ma mi lus rin chen thob pa de shin
NK100(the)012:456: tu dka' / las kyi rnam par smin pa snyegs ring pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:457: mi lus rin po che thob kyang bla ma dam pa dang mjal ba shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)012:458: bar du gcod pa'i bgegs grangs mang pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:459: bla ma dam pa dang mjal kyang bla ma dam pa'i zhabs nas 'degs pa de shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)012:460: lan chags kyi bu lon dos drag pa mang pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:461: bla ma dam pa'i zhabs nas btegs kyang zhabs thog de shes pas thongs pa shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)012:462: ser sna'i mdud pa khong dam pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:463: zhabs thog shes pas thongs kyang bla ma dam pa'i chags phyir brtson zhing 'grus pa shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)012:464: le lo dang btang snyoms gros zab pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:465: bla ma dam pa'i zhabs phyir brtson zhing 'grus par
NK100(the)012:466: byas kyang bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag go ba
NK100(the)012:468: rang gi rgyud la rtog pa'i bag chags tshan che ba'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:469: bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag go yang go thog tu nus pa shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)012:470: sems can gyi las dbang kha drag pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:471: go thog tu nus kyang thog der brtan pa shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)012:472: rig pa'i sems gya gyur mang ba'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:473: de'i phyir bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi 'bras bu thob pa shin dka' /
NK100(the)012:474: dka' ba brgyad 'phrang dam pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)012:476: mi lus thob pa dka' ba'i 'phrang la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)012:478: dang por mi lus rin po che thob par dka' ste sngar thob na bla ma'i drung du gdud /
NK100(the)012:479: ma thob na bsgrubs te thob par bya /
NK100(the)012:481: mi lus rin po che mtshon par byed pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK100(the)012:482: de bsgrub par bya ba'i thabs so //
NK100(the)012:484: rigs bzang zhing khungs btsun pa /
NK100(the)012:485: gzugs bzang zhing lta na mdzes pa /
NK100(the)012:486: gzi che zhing brjid dang ldan pa /
NK100(the)012:489: 'byor pa yo byad phun sum tshogs pa /
NK100(the)012:490: shes rab yongs su byang ba'o //
NK100(the)012:491: de bsgrub par bya ba la bsgrub thabs nyi shu
NK100(the)012:492: rtsa gcig /bdun po re re la yang 'gal rkyen
NK100(the)012:493: spangs pa / mthun rkyen brten pa /
NK100(the)012:494: cha mthun gyi spyod lam bya ba'o //
NK100(the)012:496: 'ga' ba'i rkyen nyon mongs pa nga rgyal spangs /
NK100(the)012:497: mthun pa'i rkyen zhi ba bsgom /
NK100(the)012:498: cha mthun gyi spyod lam du dge sbyor kun la brtson par bya'o //
NK100(the)012:500: nyon mongs pa khong khro spang /
NK100(the)012:502: me tog gi mchod pa rtag tu dbul //
NK100(the)012:504: nyon mongs pa phrag dog spang /
NK100(the)012:506: bla ma la mos gus cher bya /
NK100(the)012:510: sman gyi sbyin pa rtag tu dgyi /
NK100(the)012:514: tsha tsha nye 'don rtag tu bya /
NK100(the)012:516: rang gi la ser sna gzhan gyi la ma byin par len pa spang /
NK100(the)012:517: med pa drug ldan gyis tshogs sog bya /
NK100(the)012:518: kha dang lag gis sbyin pa rtag tu dgyi /
NK100(the)012:520: yul la dmigs pa med pa /
NK100(the)012:522: dad pa la 'gyur ldog med pa rdzas las zhen pa med pa /
NK100(the)012:523: rjes la rlom pa med pa /
NK100(the)012:524: mtha' la khyad pa med pa /
NK100(the)012:525: shes rab yongs su byang ba la gzhan shes rab gsum sbyong ba la bar chad mi bya /
NK100(the)012:526: rang shes rab gsum la sbyang /
NK100(the)012:527: mar me'i mched pa rtag tu dbul lo //
NK100(the)012:528: bla ma dam pa dang mjal ba dka' ste /
NK100(the)012:529: sngar mjal na zhabs nas 'degs par bya /
NK100(the)012:530: ma mjal na bar chad dbang du mi gtong drug tu phyir la mjal /
NK100(the)012:532: sngar bteg na shes pas thongs par bya /
NK100(the)012:533: ma btegs na lan chags dbang du mi gtang mnyes
NK100(the)012:534: pa phul la 'deg /shes pas ma thong pa dka'
NK100(the)012:535: ste / sngar btang na chags phyir brtson 'grus bya /
NK100(the)012:536: ma btang na ser sna'i dbang du mi btang 'dzin chags med par thong /
NK100(the)012:537: brtson zhing 'grus par dka' ste sngar brtson zhing 'grus na go bar bya /
NK100(the)012:538: brtson zhing ma 'grus na le lo'i dbang du mi gtang rjes 'brang brtson 'grus bya /
NK100(the)012:539: gdams ngag go bar dka' ste sngar go na go thog tu nus par bya /
NK100(the)012:540: ma go na bag chags dbang du mi gtang thugs dgongs go bar bya /
NK100(the)012:541: go thog tu nus pa dka' ste /
NK100(the)012:542: sngar nus na nus thog brtan par bya /
NK100(the)012:543: ma nus na las dbang du mi gtang /
NK100(the)012:545: nus thog tu brtan pa dka' ste sngar brtan na 'bras bu thob par bya /
NK100(the)012:546: mi brtan na gya gyu'i dbang du mi gtang /
NK100(the)012:549: sngar thob na 'gro ba'i don bya /
NK100(the)012:550: ma thob na 'phrang brgyad du mi gtang ste /
NK100(the)012:552: dbugs phar 'gro ba ni rtsol ba /
NK100(the)012:553: tshur 'du ba ni srog ces bya'o //
NK100(the)012:554: tshur 'dus ba'i dus su byang chub sems kyi bde
NK100(the)012:555: ba dkar breng gis byung nas thig le la phog
NK100(the)012:556: pas / sol ba'i me la phus gtab pa bzhin du dka' wal tser byung /
NK100(the)012:558: des lus mgo mjug dga' bas khengs par byas pa'o //
NK100(the)012:560: dang po 'jug pa'i sgo dgag ste /
NK100(the)012:561: bdag gis ral gri 'am spu gri thogs par bsams te /
NK100(the)012:562: des ske bcad par bsams la /
NK100(the)012:565: kun d+har ma gsum sbu gu sang nge yod par bsam /
NK100(the)012:566: rang gi lag pas spyi bo nas mnan pas rtsa gsum gyi kha bcad par bsams la /
NK100(the)012:567: nag mun tser song bar bsal mo //
NK100(the)012:569: rang gi snying gshags par bsams la /
NK100(the)012:570: der rnam rtog 'gyu ba bcug nas sbyar bas /
NK100(the)012:571: rnam rtog gis mi thar te /
NK100(the)012:572: de nas thar kyang byang khog nas mi thar bar bsam pa'o //
NK100(the)012:573: gnas pa'i phugs btib pa ni /
NK100(the)012:574: rnam rtog gi rten snying yin pas snying rtsar gyis bton nas bskyur bar bsam pa'o //
NK100(the)012:575: rang gi khong pa stong sang nge yod par bsams te /
NK100(the)012:576: de ni gsang sngags thabs che ba yin pas /
NK100(the)012:577: yin pa rnam rtog yin te /
NK100(the)012:580: khyi gus khyi gu 'byin pa dang 'dra'o //
NK100(the)012:581: rgod pa ma rungs par gyur na bya'o //
NK100(the)012:582: de med na mi dgos lta bas bcos pas chog gsung /
NK100(the)012:583: byang chub sems kyi btsal thabs gsum ni /
NK100(the)012:584: rta rmu rgod lta btsal ba ni /
NK100(the)012:585: rta rmu rgod mi bsrun pa kha then na slar la thu ste /
NK100(the)012:586: skyes bu stobs dang ldan pas lcag gis brabs nas
NK100(the)012:587: gar 'gro 'gror btang nas gzhugs 'chad pa bzhin du
NK100(the)012:588: / shes pa 'phro na mi bzung par gar 'gro 'gror btang na slar ldog pa'o //
NK100(the)012:589: rin po che'i gter ltar btsal ba ni /
NK100(the)012:591: rkun mos mi rnyed de nam dgos pa'i dus su spyad du 'ong /
NK100(the)012:592: de bzhin du dang po bsgom legs pas /
NK100(the)012:593: bzhug cir snang thams cad bsgom par shes pa'o //
NK100(the)012:594: rgyal po'i btsun mo ltar btsa' ba ni /
NK100(the)012:595: rgyal po'i mnga' 'og tu thams cad 'dus pas /
NK100(the)012:596: btsun mo la yid 'chor kyang spyod mi nus pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)012:597: thams cad chos nyid du shes tsa na rnam rtog ldang mi nus pa'o //
NK100(the)012:599: gsal ba'i tshad til gyi mar me ltar bu ni /
NK100(the)012:600: mar me la gsal byed gzhan gyis gsal bar byas pa med de /
NK100(the)012:601: kho rang gsal ba de bzhin du /
NK100(the)012:603: dkar sa le ba lta bu min te /
NK100(the)012:604: yul med du sang nge sa le ba'o //
NK100(the)012:605: mi g.yo ba'i tshad rgya mtsho'i gting lta bu ni /
NK100(the)012:606: rgya mtsho'i kha 'dom dgu yan chad g.yo yang /
NK100(the)012:607: gting mi g.yo ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)012:608: rnam rtog gang yang mi g.yo bar me re lteng nge ba'o //
NK100(the)012:609: yang zhing 'jam pa'i tshad shing bal gyi 'dab ma lta bu ni /
NK100(the)012:612: phyi'i drod lus yod du mi tshor ba dang /
NK100(the)012:613: nang gi drod dbugs rgyu ba mi tshor ba dang /
NK100(the)012:614: gsang ba'i drod rtog med kyi bde ba rang la 'char ba'o //
NK100(the)012:617: phyi'i rtags lung ston 'byung ba ni /
NK100(the)012:618: rigs kyi bu khyod kyi lta ba la skyon 'di 'dug /bsgrub pa'i gnas ni 'di yin /
NK100(the)012:619: khyod kyis spyod pa bya ba'i dus la bab po la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)012:620: nang gi rtags mngon shes 'byung ste /
NK100(the)012:621: rig pa dwangs snyigs phyed pas so //
NK100(the)012:622: gsang ba'i rtags snang ba lam du blangs pa'o //
NK100(the)012:623: lnga pa bsgom snang bcu tham pas bsgom mkhan ngos bzung ba ni /
NK100(the)012:624: gong ltar bsgom par byang pas nyams 'byung ngo //
NK100(the)012:631: lus stong par yod pa snyam byed pa dang /
NK100(the)012:632: med pa snyam byed pa dang /
NK100(the)012:633: dum bur yod pa snyam byed pa ste /
NK100(the)012:634: zhi gnas shas che ba las 'byung gsung ngo //
NK100(the)012:636: sa le ba snyam byed pa dang //
NK100(the)012:637: khyim la sogs pa sa le ba snyam byed pa'o //
NK100(the)012:638: sangs kyis song ba snyam byed pa na /
NK100(the)012:639: shes pa sangs rgyas song ba snyam byed pa'o //
NK100(the)012:640: phyad kyis song ba snyam byed pa ni /
NK100(the)012:641: shes pa phyad kyis song pa snyam byed pa'o //
NK100(the)012:642: gsang ba'i bsgom snang gsum ni /
NK100(the)012:643: me re yod pa snyam byed pa /
NK100(the)012:644: khyil le yod pa snyam byed pa /
NK100(the)012:647: rig pa rang sar grol ba ste /
NK100(the)012:648: snang srid thams cad rang grol ba 'di gal che gsung ngo //
NK100(the)012:649: drug pa bskyed 'don gsum gyis bogs gdon pa ni /
NK100(the)012:650: gong ltar bsgom pa byas pas /
NK100(the)012:651: dus thams cad du phyam tser ma song na bskyed gdon te /
NK100(the)012:654: snang ba dang sems la spyad par bya ba dang /
NK100(the)012:656: lta ba'i thog tu btang gi bsgoms na bogs 'ong ngo //
NK100(the)012:657: spyod pas bogs gdon pa ni /
NK100(the)012:658: gsang spyod dang rigs spyod ces bya ste /
NK100(the)012:660: dgon pa dben par lus gcer bu la sogs pa byas la /
NK100(the)012:661: nyam nga zhing bsgom pa la gnas sam mi gnas lta /
NK100(the)012:662: mi gnas na bsgom pa rang bya /
NK100(the)012:663: gnas na rigs spyod ces bya ste /
NK100(the)012:664: spyod pa bya bar rigs te /
NK100(the)012:665: gzod grong dang tshong dus su phyin nas /
NK100(the)012:666: gong bzhin du byas pa nyam nga mi 'dug na /
NK100(the)012:667: gzod phyag rgya mo dang sbyor ba dang /
NK100(the)012:668: sgrol ba la sogs pa'i spyod pa bya ba'i dus la bab pa'o //
NK100(the)012:669: kha zas kyis bogs gdon pa ni /
NK100(the)012:670: 'khams la phan pa'i zas bzang po bza' ba'o //
NK100(the)012:671: bdun pa shes pa bzhis bdud bzhi gzhom pa ni /
NK100(the)012:672: nyon mongs pa'i bdud lam du shes pa ste /
NK100(the)012:673: rnal 'byor pas nyon mongs pa ci byung yang /
NK100(the)012:674: mi dgag mi spang ste chos nyid du shes pa'o //
NK100(the)012:675: phung po'i bdud sgyu mar shes pa ni /
NK100(the)012:676: rnal 'byor pas phung po khyod 'dra ba /
NK100(the)012:679: khyi ltogs spyang ltogs kyi zas su nam kyang 'gro
NK100(the)012:680: ba cig 'dug /bkur sti byas kyi thu ba cig
NK100(the)012:681: 'dug pas / chos spyod la bkol ba'i phyir zas
NK100(the)012:682: dum 'ga' tsam bza' ba las snyam par sgyu mar
NK100(the)012:684: phung po la chags zhen med pas phung po'i bdud bcom mo //
NK100(the)012:685: lha'i bu bdud grogs su shes pa ste /
NK100(the)012:686: bdud kyi spyod yul ci byung yang grogs su shes pa'o //
NK100(the)012:687: 'chi bdag gi bdud shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin par shes pa ni /
NK100(the)012:689: brgyad pa bsre thabs gsum gyis bsgom pa bdag po la gtad pa ni /
NK100(the)012:690: nyin mo'i dus su las dang so nam dang bsre ba ni /
NK100(the)012:691: las su bya ba'i zhing yul lta bu yang rang bzhin med de rang gi sems /
NK100(the)012:692: bdag kyang rang bzhin med par shes pa'o //
NK100(the)012:693: nub mo'i dus su gnyid dang bsre ba ni /
NK100(the)012:694: da bsgom gtang la gnyid log bya ba med par /
NK100(the)012:695: gnyid log kyi yang bsgoms pas /
NK100(the)012:696: gnyid log tsam na yang bsgom pa las mi 'da' ste /
NK100(the)012:697: rmi lam rgyun 'chad do gsung ngo //
NK100(the)012:698: 'chi ba'i dus su 'chi ba dang bsre ba ni /
NK100(the)012:699: 'chi' kar gdab pa'i dus su gsal lo //
NK100(the)012:700: dgu pa sa bzhis gol sa bcad pa ni /
NK100(the)012:701: bying rgod bcos pas so so skye bo'i gol sa gcod do //
NK100(the)012:702: stong pa yin no snyam pa'i blos gzung du bsgoms na /
NK100(the)012:703: mu stegs chad lta yin te /
NK100(the)012:704: blos bzung nyid rang sar grol te 'dzin pa med pas chad pa'i gol sa gcod do //
NK100(the)012:705: bsam gtan mu bzhi'i gol sa yang blos bzung nyid rang sar grol bas chod do //
NK100(the)012:706: theg pa chen po bsam gtan gyi gol sa ni /
NK100(the)012:707: dbu ma dang sems tsam yin te snang ba la 'dra legs byas nas bsgom pa ste /
NK100(the)012:708: 'dir gti bya ltar bsgoms pas chod do //
NK100(the)012:709: bcu pa phan yon bzhi sa yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK100(the)012:711: bon chog brgya byas pas bsgom pa thun gcig daga'o //
NK100(the)012:712: tshe yun gyi phan yon ni /
NK100(the)012:713: skye ba thams cad du byang chub thob par byed
NK100(the)012:714: pa'i thabs bsgom pa 'di las snang nye ba'i thabs
NK100(the)012:715: gzhan med pa'o // yon tan thams cad 'dus pa'i phan yon ni /
NK100(the)012:716: dkar po'i chos spyod thams cad kyi phan yon 'dir 'dus pa'o //
NK100(the)012:717: tshegs chung la don che ba'i phan yon ni /
NK100(the)012:718: tshegs chung ste nyams su lon na /
NK100(the)012:720: don che ste bla med thob pa'o //
NK100(the)012:722: shes rab dang mthun pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK100(the)012:723: lta bsgom phyams kyis song na /
NK100(the)012:724: dge ba dang du blang du med /
NK100(the)012:725: sdig pa rgyab tu bskyur du med /
NK100(the)012:727: dge ba la yang rang bzhin med par shes /
NK100(the)012:728: sdig pa la yang rang bzhin med par shes /
NK100(the)012:729: dbang po rab kyi spyod yul lo //
NK100(the)012:731: bsnyon pa lta bu'i spyod pa ni /
NK100(the)012:732: zas la gtsang sme med pa /
NK100(the)012:733: gos la bzang ngan med pa /
NK100(the)012:734: sems la dga' mi dga' med pa'o //
NK100(the)012:735: bu chung lta ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK100(the)012:740: de bzhin du spyod pa la blang dor med /
NK100(the)012:744: lkugs pa lta bu'i spyod pa ni /
NK100(the)012:745: mi chos kyi smra ba la sogs pa ci yang mi byed par 'dug pa /
NK100(the)012:747: de dbang po rab kyi spyod pa ste /
NK100(the)012:748: lta ba gza' gtad med pas spyod pa blang dor med pa'o //
NK100(the)012:749: thabs dang mthun pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK100(the)012:750: gong ltar lta bsgom phyams kyis ma song na /
NK100(the)012:751: spyod pa dge sdig shan phyeed pa zhes bya ste /
NK100(the)012:754: dge sbyor la sogs pa chos dang mthun par bya'o //
NK100(the)012:755: sgo gsum rgyud kyi spyod pa ni /
NK100(the)012:756: g.yo med zog med ma bcos shugs las byung ba'o //
NK100(the)012:757: le lo can gyi gang zag la 'chi kar gdab pa ni /
NK100(the)012:758: rjes su dran pa drug go //
NK100(the)012:759: 'chi ba rjes su dran pa ni /
NK100(the)012:760: so so skye bo nam shi shir nam 'chi cha med pas /
NK100(the)012:761: rnal 'byor pas na tsa na brtag ste /
NK100(the)012:762: dang po sa chu la thim ste /
NK100(the)012:763: bag gzhi sa la lhung lus lci ba'o //
NK100(the)012:764: de la 'chi ba'i dngos gzhi yang med /
NK100(the)012:765: de nas chu me la thim ste /
NK100(the)012:766: drod phyir thon pa'am nang gi chu skams pa ste /
NK100(the)012:767: kha sna skam sing gis song pa'o //
NK100(the)012:769: drod yan lag nas bsdus te /
NK100(the)012:770: spyi bo nas brdul te rkang mthil du yal na nang /
NK100(the)012:771: spyi bor yal na bzang ngo //
NK100(the)012:772: rlung rnam par shes pa la thim ste /
NK100(the)012:774: tshul 'du ba srog ste srog chad 'dod pas /
NK100(the)012:775: phar thon nas tshur nang du 'ong du mi 'dod de srog 'chad pa'o //
NK100(the)012:776: de ni 'chi ba rjes su dran pa'o //
NK100(the)012:777: skyo ba rjes su dran pa ni /
NK100(the)012:778: zhing yul khang khyim la sogs pa 'di dag thams cad sgyu ma yin /
NK100(the)012:779: nangs na nye ba'i rang gi lus po 'dir rang yang mi rtag pa /
NK100(the)012:781: sdug bsngal bskyed pa'i gzhi ma cig 'dug snyam pa bskyed de /
NK100(the)012:782: so so'i skye bo ni 'chi ba'i dus su /
NK100(the)012:783: shin tu chags pas 'khor bar ltung /
NK100(the)012:784: rnal 'byor pas de las bzlog las gong ltar bya'o //
NK100(the)012:785: gtong ba rjes su dran pa ni /
NK100(the)012:786: gnyen 'dun la sogs 'di dag thams cad gnas skabs kyi 'brel ba bya dang shing lta bu yin /
NK100(the)012:787: nga dang po 'ongs kyang gcig pu 'ongs /
NK100(the)012:788: tha ma mchi yang gcig pu 'chi snyam pas /
NK100(the)012:789: thams cad dang 'brel med yin snyam pas ma chags par phyad tsher gtong ba'o //
NK100(the)012:790: lha rjes su dran pa ni /
NK100(the)012:792: 'di'i gnas skabs su lha yang chos sku ste /
NK100(the)012:793: de yang rang gi sems stong par bsgom pa de dran par bya /
NK100(the)012:795: gong na med na 'dir gdab pa gdab ste dka' gsung ngo //
NK100(the)012:796: bar do rjes su dran pa ni /
NK100(the)012:797: srid pa'i bar ma do ces bya ste /
NK100(the)012:798: snang ba 'di nub phyi ma'i lus gzhan ma blangs
NK100(the)012:799: kyi bar du yid kyi lus gnas pa de'i dus
NK100(the)012:800: su / kha gsum sprad pa'i man ngag ces bya ste /
NK100(the)012:802: bar do dang 'chi ba shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa gsum 'dzom ste /
NK100(the)012:803: bar do'i dus su gsang sngags gseb lam nas 'gro ba zhes bya ste /
NK100(the)012:804: yid sngar nas bsgom pa dang ma bral bas /
NK100(the)012:805: 'chi ba shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa dang 'dzom nas /
NK100(the)012:806: bar do la mi rtog dran nas skye ba mi len te /
NK100(the)012:807: 'di'i rnam rtog pas rmi lam gyi rnam rtog bzlog sla /
NK100(the)012:808: de bas bar do sla ste /
NK100(the)012:809: bar do la mi rtog pa dran pa tsam gyis sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK100(the)012:810: 'chi ba shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa rjes su dran pa ni /
NK100(the)012:811: dbugs chad pa'i dus su ma rtog pa skad cig ma gcig kun la skye /
NK100(the)012:812: de ngo shes pa ni dran pa'o //
NK100(the)012:814: skye ba len mi len gyi khyad par bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)012:815: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyab 'gyel bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)012:816: sangs rgya ba'i dus bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)012:817: sangs rgyas bya ba ji tsam cig la zer ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)012:818: dang po ni grags pa'i chos brgyad dang ma bral na skye ba len /
NK100(the)012:821: rang gzung 'dzin dang bral ma bral lta'o //
NK100(the)012:823: lhun grub chos kyi sku'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK100(the)012:824: stong gsal rig pa chos kyi sku'i sangs rgyas ste /
NK100(the)012:826: shi ba'i dus su sdig po che man chad la mi rtog pa gcig skye'o //
NK100(the)012:829: bag chags nying 'tshams sbyor ba ni /
NK100(the)012:830: kun gzhi la bag chags gnas pa de'o //
NK100(the)012:832: bag chags de las rig pa 'gyu byed langs nas bar do 'khyams pa'o //
NK100(the)012:833: phung po nying 'tshams sbyor ba ni /
NK100(the)012:834: der bag chags 'gyus pas byol song du skye na /
NK100(the)012:835: byol song gi mngal nyams dga' bar mthong nas /
NK100(the)012:836: der zhugs pas subs tser song nas lus len pa'o //
NK100(the)012:837: mya ngan las 'das par rgyab 'gyes na /
NK100(the)012:838: stong gsum rig pa chos kyi sku'i sangs rgyas zhes bya ste /
NK100(the)012:839: mi rtog pa de ka'i thog nas grol yang srid /
NK100(the)012:840: de min bar do la chos nyid dran pas sangs rgya ba'o //
NK100(the)012:841: sangs rgya ba'i dus bstan pa ni /
NK100(the)012:842: rab 'di la rgya ste rgyal ba'i dgongs pa rtogs pa'o //
NK100(the)012:844: 'chi ba shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa
NK100(the)012:845: dang 'brel nas mi rtog par 'gro ste sangs rgya'o
NK100(the)012:846: // de 'og bar do la rgya ste /
NK100(the)012:847: bar ma do la chos nyid dran nas so //
NK100(the)012:848: tha ma yang skye ba gcig gam gnyis sam bdun tshun chad du sangs rgya'o //
NK100(the)012:849: sangs rgyas bya ba ji tsam cig la bya na /
NK100(the)012:850: chos kyi sku ni sangs rgyas te /
NK100(the)012:851: rang gi rig pa stong gsal du bsgom pa de'o //
NK100(the)012:852: gzugs sku ni de'i byin gyis brlabs las 'gro ba'i don du sku gnyis byin te /
NK100(the)012:853: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' la longs sku'o //
NK100(the)012:854: las dag pa'i sems can la sprul skus don byed do //
NK100(the)012:855: des gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyi snyan khung brgyud
NK100(the)012:856: pa'i gdams ngag /snyan brgyud yi ger bris pa lags
NK100(the)012:857: pas / gzhan la mi spel lo //
NK100(the)012:860: rta rin chen dpal gyi phyag dape'o //
